        "content": "<p>alexcrichton requested <a href=\"https://github.com/orgs/bytecodealliance/teams/wasmtime-wasi-reviewers\">wasmtime-wasi-reviewers</a> for a review on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12748\">PR #12748</a>.</p>",
